rows.label: qst701506_msg0004
rows.name:
His breathing sounds strange...
There might be something
wrong with his airway.

rows.label: qst701506_msg0005
rows.name:
What should we do? What if
it's some kind of seizure?

rows.label: qst701506_msg0006
rows.name: Shall I go call a doctor?

rows.label: qst701506_msg0007
rows.name:
No, from here, we might
not make it in time.

rows.label: qst701506_msg0008
rows.name: We'll have to perform first aid.

rows.label: qst701506_msg0010
rows.name:
Something to soothe his throat
would help. We need to make it
easier for him to breathe...
